TITLE: Template Locking in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to implement template locking to prevent block manipulation. This example locks all operations on a paragraph block template.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wordpress/gutenberg/blob/trunk/docs/reference-guides/block-api/block-templates.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
function myplugin_register_template() {
	$post_type_object = get_post_type_object( 'post' );
	$post_type_object->template = array(
		array( 'core/paragraph', array(
			'placeholder' => 'Add Description...',
		) ),
	);
	$post_type_object->template_lock = 'all';
}
add_action( 'init', 'myplugin_register_template' );
```

