TITLE: Using Templates in InnerBlocks
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code snippet demonstrates how to set up a default block template for InnerBlocks. The template specifies a predefined arrangement of blocks, including their attributes and placeholders, such as columns comprising an image and a paragraph with a placeholder. This allows predefined initial states for InnerBlocks.
