TITLE: Using BoxControl Component in React
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to use the BoxControl component in a React functional component. It shows setting up initial values and handling changes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wordpress/gutenberg/blob/trunk/packages/components/src/box-control/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
import { useState } from 'react';
import { BoxControl } from '@wordpress/components';

function Example() {
  const [ values, setValues ] = useState( {
    top: '50px',
    left: '10%',
    right: '10%',
    bottom: '50px',
  } );

  return (
    <BoxControl
      __next40pxDefaultSize
      values={ values }
      onChange={ setValues }
    />
  );
};
```

