TITLE: Implementing Basic Slot/Fill Pattern with SlotFillProvider in React
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use SlotFillProvider, Slot, and Fill components together to enable portal rendering. The example creates a panel with a slot that can be filled from elsewhere in the component tree.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wordpress/gutenberg/blob/trunk/packages/components/src/slot-fill/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
import {
	SlotFillProvider,
	Slot,
	Fill,
	Panel,
	PanelBody,
} from '@wordpress/components';

const MySlotFillProvider = () => {
	const MyPanelSlot = () => (
		<Panel header="Panel with slot">
			<PanelBody>
				<Slot name="MyPanelSlot" />
			</PanelBody>
		</Panel>
	);

	MyPanelSlot.Content = () => <Fill name="MyPanelSlot">Panel body</Fill>;

	return (
		<SlotFillProvider>
			<MyPanelSlot />
			<MyPanelSlot.Content />
		</SlotFillProvider>
	);
};
```

