TITLE: Implementing Block Toolbar Controls in WordPress Gutenberg
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to add custom controls to the Block Toolbar using the BlockControls component. It includes an AlignmentToolbar for text alignment and a RichText component for content editing.
