TITLE: Locking paragraph block position
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet utilizes the `blocks.getBlockAttributes` filter to lock the position of all paragraph blocks on a page. It checks if the block type is `core/paragraph` and, if so, adds a `lock` attribute to prevent moving the block.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wordpress/gutenberg/blob/trunk/docs/reference-guides/filters/block-filters.md#2025-04-21_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// Our filter function
function lockParagraphs( blockAttributes, blockType, innerHTML, attributes  ) {
    if('core/paragraph' === blockType.name) {
        blockAttributes['lock'] = {move: true}
    }
    return blockAttributes;
}

// Add the filter
wp.hooks.addFilter(
    'blocks.getBlockAttributes',
    'my-plugin/lock-paragraphs',
    lockParagraphs
);

```

