TITLE: Using useDropZone with Wrapper Element in React
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to use the `useDropZone` hook with a wrapper element. A state variable `dropZoneElement` is used to hold a reference to the outer wrapper, and this reference is passed to the `useDropZone` hook. The drop zone functionality is applied to the inner div, which is a descendant of the outer wrapper.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wordpress/gutenberg/blob/trunk/packages/compose/src/hooks/use-drop-zone/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

