SOURCE: https://github.com/wordpress/gutenberg/blob/trunk/docs/how-to-guides/data-basics/1-data-basics-setup.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { createRoot } from 'react-dom';
import './style.css';

function MyFirstApp() {
	return <span>Hello from JavaScript!</span>;
}

const root = createRoot( document.getElementById( 'my-first-gutenberg-app' ) );
window.addEventListener(
	'load',
	function () {
		root.render(
			<MyFirstApp />,
		);
	},
	false
);
```

