TITLE: PHP Block Bindings Value Filter
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of a filter to modify block binding values, specifically formatting visualization dates with fallback handling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wordpress/gutenberg/blob/trunk/docs/reference-guides/block-api/block-bindings.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
function wpmovies_format_visualization_date( $value, $name ) {
	if ( $name !== 'wpmovies/visualization-date' ) {
		return $value;
	}
	if ( ! $value ) {
		return date( 'm/d/Y' );
	}
	return date( 'm/d/Y', strtotime( $value ) );
}

add_filter( 'block_bindings_source_value', 'wpmovies_format_visualization_date', 10, 2 );
```

