TITLE: PHP: Defining Computed Initial State
DESCRIPTION: Defines the initial state on the server using the `wp_interactivity_state` function in PHP, computing the value of `hasFruits` based on the initial `fruits` array. This approach is useful when the derived state depends on other server-side variables or computations.
