TITLE: Disabling and enabling tips programmatically
DESCRIPTION: This JSX snippet shows how to use the `disableTips` and `enableTips` dispatch methods, along with the `areTipsEnabled` selector, from the `core/nux` data store to programmatically control the state of tips. The button's text and action change based on whether tips are currently enabled or disabled.
