TITLE: Adding POST Method Support for ServerSideRender in PHP
DESCRIPTION: PHP function to add POST method support for the ServerSideRender component in WordPress versions earlier than 5.5. This allows sending attributes in the request body instead of the URL.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wordpress/gutenberg/blob/trunk/packages/server-side-render/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
function add_rest_method( $endpoints ) {
    if ( is_wp_version_compatible( '5.5' ) ) {
        return $endpoints;
    }

    foreach ( $endpoints as $route => $handler ) {
        if ( isset( $endpoints[ $route ][0] ) ) {
            $endpoints[ $route ][0]['methods'] = [ WP_REST_Server::READABLE, WP_REST_Server::CREATABLE ];
        }
    }

    return $endpoints;
}
add_filter( 'rest_endpoints', 'add_rest_method');
```

