TITLE: Implementing FocalPointPicker Component in React with WordPress Gutenberg
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to implement the FocalPointPicker component in a React application. It shows state management for the focal point, rendering the component, and applying the resulting values to CSS styles for background positioning.
