TITLE: Ensuring Class Name for List Blocks with blocks.registerBlockType Filter in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet uses the blocks.registerBlockType filter to ensure that List blocks are saved with the canonical generated class name (wp-block-list).
SOURCE: https://github.com/wordpress/gutenberg/blob/trunk/docs/reference-guides/filters/block-filters.md#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function addListBlockClassName( settings, name ) {
	if ( name !== 'core/list' ) {
		return settings;
	}

	return {
		...settings,
		supports: {
			...settings.supports,
			className: true,
		},
	};
}

wp.hooks.addFilter(
	'blocks.registerBlockType',
	'my-plugin/class-names/list-block',
	addListBlockClassName
);
```

