LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
function myguten_content_filter( $content ) {
	$value = get_post_meta( get_the_ID(), 'myguten_meta_block_field', true );
	if ( $value ) {
		return sprintf( "%s <h4> %s </h4>", $content, esc_html( $value ) );
	} else {
		return $content;
	}
}
add_filter( 'the_content', 'myguten_content_filter' );
```

