TITLE: Modifying Theme JSON Data with wp_theme_json_data_theme Filter in PHP
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use the wp_theme_json_data_theme filter to modify the theme's color palette and disable the text color UI. It creates a new data array with updated color settings and uses the update_with() method to apply the changes.
