## 2.19.0 (2025-02-28)

### Bug Fixes

-   Revert "Handle styles assets on region-based navigation". ([#69222](https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/pull/69222))

## 2.18.0 (2025-02-12)

### Bug Fixes

